    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span dir=\"ltr\">Common clothing made through basic tailoring.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\"> Most sets of clothing are considered Commoners clothes, but can be broken up into different categories based on the quality of said clothing.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\"> While still counting as unarmored for the purpose as calculating AC, better quality clothing can provide benefits based on those being interacted with, while wearing such clothes.</span></p><p></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">Advantage on all ability checks or saving throws as a result of a cold environment.</span></p>",
